<h3>Systems for Monitoring</h3>
<p>The "S" in HEARTS stands for "Systems for monitoring." We are supporting monitoring systems to improve the efficacy of hypertension treatment projects. Resolve to Save Lives is guiding the <a href="http://simple.org">Simple.org</a> project to build a focused tool for healthcare workers to monitor their high blood pressure patients over time. We are also building dashboards to help administrators to oversee their programs in close to real time. And, our informatics experts help countries to integrate their systems effectively so leaders can get on the same page.</p>

